---
import safety from "../assets/image/safety.png";
const { title, paragraph, button, navTips1, navTips2, navTips3, navTips4, navTips5, link1, link2, link3, link4, link5 } = Astro.props;
---

<div class="section">
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href={link1}>{navTips1}</a></li>
      <li><a href={link2}>{navTips2}</a></li>
      <li><a href={link3}>{navTips3}</a></li>
      <li><a href={link4}>{navTips4}</a></li>
      <li><a href={link5}>{navTips5}</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>
</div>
<div class="title-content">
  <h2>safety</h2>
  <div class="underline"></div>
  <p>En <strong>La95 Trucking Show</strong> sabemos que la seguridad es lo más importante en la industria del transporte. 
    Contamos con especialistas que pueden orientarte en todos los aspectos de <em>Safety</em>, desde la prevención de accidentes 
    hasta el cumplimiento de regulaciones. Agenda tu consulta personalizada y recibe asesoría experta para tu empresa o proyecto.</p>
</div>
<figure> 
  <ul>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>Bus Safety – Look Before You Book</li>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>Household Goods – Protect Your Move</li>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>Driver Safety</li>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>Passenger Carrier Safety</li>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>Company Safety Data</li>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>Highway-Rail Grade Crossing Safety</li>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>Commercial Tire Safety Tips</li>
    <li><i class="ph ph-check"></i>CMV Traffic Safety Facts</li>
  </ul>
  <img src={safety.src} alt="">
</figure>


<style lang="scss">
  @use "../assets/sass/index" as *;
   // start new styles

  nav ul{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .title-content >p {
    margin: 20px 5%;
  }

  figure {
    display: flex;
    margin: 20px 5%;
    border: 2px solid $accent-b-light;
    border-radius: 8px;
    img {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  a {
    color: $secondary;
  }

  li:hover {
    text-decoration:underline;
    text-decoration-color: $accent-b-light;
    text-underline-offset: 13px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 3px;
  }

  .section-center {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 30px;
  }

  .light-gold {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    width: 145px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }

   button{
    color: $accent-b-dark;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: $regular;
    font-family: $heading;
    background-color: $tertiary;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .light-gold.gold-button {
    background-color: $tertiary;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px 10px rgba($accent-b-dark, 35%);
    border: 2px solid $accent-b-dark;
    margin: 20px 0 30px;
  }

  .gold-button {
    background-color: $accent-b-light;
  }

  .gold-button:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 0 25px 15px rgba($accent-b-light, 40%);
  }

   ul{
    font-family: $text;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 2.5;
    font-weight: $regular;
    color: white;
    padding: 0;
  }

  i{
    color: $accent-b-dark;
    margin: 10px;
  }

  li {
    margin: 10px;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;

    li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-family: $text;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: white;

      i {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #FFCC4D;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      span {
        display: block;
        flex: 1;
      }
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1025px) {
    figure {
      justify-content: space-between;
      width: 50%;
      img {
        display: block;
        width: 300px;
        min-width: 50px;
        object-fit: contain;
      }
    }

    .section {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background-color: $primary;

      h2 {
        font-size: 3rem;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
      }
      a {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
    }

    ul {
      gap: 50px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    nav {
      margin: 0 15%;
    }

    .light-gold {
      width: 178px;
    }
  }
</style>